<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="gossip-n">gossip <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡɒsɪp/    美 /'ɡɑːsɪp/  </p>
<p>[U] &amp; [C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>闲话；流言；[C] 闲聊：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I never spread gossip.
我从不传播流言蜚语。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have a gossip with friends
与朋友闲聊</p></div></div>